This year Surf Camp Australia is offering two unique 7- Day Christmas and New years camps. These camps are not the same as our traditional “ 7-Day – The Search” adventure, it’s a one-time yearly special that takes the fantastic experience of our “5-Day – Ultimate Experience” and extends it over 7 days!⁠
You can still deck the halls with surfboards and wetsuits, escaping accommodation in the city and spending Christmas or New years down south at Stunning Seven Mile Beach with the Surf Camp Australia team!⁠
Get down to Surf Camp for an experience of a lifetime and spend your holiday by the beach with friends, surfing and sunshine!⁠
⁠
This holiday adventure includes everything you need:⁠
⁠
There’s no better holiday than a true blue Aussie Christmas!⁠
⁠
(22-29 December 2023 / Friday to Friday)⁠
SURF: 7 Day Progressive Surf Course for Absolute Beginners⁠
GEAR: All Surfing Equipment – Rip Curl Wetsuits & Surfboards⁠
STAY: 7 Nights in Modern Beachside Accommodation⁠
MEALS: All Meals Provided⁠
Surf Lessons: 11x 2 Hours Surf lessons (Surf every day except Christmas Day)⁠
TRAVEL: Transport from Sydney included (Friday 6pm Pick up and drop off)⁠
PHOTOS and VIDEO: Surfing Photography and Video during 7day course⁠
⁠
or⁠
⁠
Experience New Year’s by the beach!⁠
⁠
(29 December 2023 – 5 January 2024/ Friday to Friday)⁠
SURF: 7 Day Progressive Surf Course for Absolute Beginners⁠
GEAR: All Surfing Equipment – Rip Curl Wetsuits & Surfboards⁠
STAY: 7 Nights in Modern Beachside Accommodation⁠
MEALS: All Meals Provided⁠
Surf Lessons: 11x 2 Hours Surf lessons⁠
TRAVEL: Transport from Sydney included (Friday 6pm Pick up and drop off)⁠
PHOTOS and VIDEOS: Surfing Photography and Video during 7day course⁠
⁠
For only 1195$
